{"tid":610650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[IT狗] HK Express 復活假前一度死官網！只因沒有查電郵？","createTime":"2018-03-30T07:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T11:49:26.000Z","uid":42188,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4e32fc5e78c3300842c73b829a0bf96647ba3f47","tid":610650,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"終於到了大家都期待已久的長假期，不少人都會選擇外遊。然而，廉價航空香港快運（HK Express）的官方網站卻在復活假期前突然無法登入，連帶導致網上預辦登機服務也需暫停，引起不少客人鼓噪。然而據業界人士推測，這次「死官網」並不是偶然，這可能是 <span style=\"color: red;\">HK Express 的 IT 部門</span>忘了查電郵確認網域管理人資料所致！<br />\n<br />\n由於連接港快運官網（<a href=\"http://www.hkexpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkexpress.com&d=yY4n0Etsvt53l5azvnt8Zm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=507e4bfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.hkexpress.com</a>）後，會跳出「This domain has been redirected.」的字眼，估計是 HK Express 未有按照網域監管機構 ICANN 的要求，進行 WHOIS 網域管理人資料確認所致。原來，網絡登記商需要每隔幾年向用戶確認網域管理人資料。多半會發出附有確認連接的自動電郵，簡單花數分鐘就能完成資料確認。因此，今次有可能是 IT 部門沒有查電郵，導致整個網域被上鎖，其後亦無法即時修復網站。"},{"pid":"22a28e6cbd0439b372b7b35c47f2b589eedfffd0","tid":610650,"uid":4525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"it 唔使放假咩"},{"pid":"e5f5871a14a4e5e8781b40ebb4d730823251e87c","tid":610650,"uid":25858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"IT 奴工又食死貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a770b65da21bfbdea8ed14585c76c00657767c67","tid":610650,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> IT"},{"pid":"58325d00fca0975d4252eb2ad333071ade8a2ac2","tid":610650,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"molamola <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一車車IT狗運緊去屠房，流緊眼淚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3932e482ac96640f3586e9ef2c548ea5c638204","tid":610650,"uid":36551,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:29:04.000Z","msg":"IT狗俾人炒 &gt; 奴工市場出現一大班IT狗 &gt; 其他公司低價吸納 &gt; 請咗新人就炒咗本身啲高年資高薪IT狗 &gt; 奴工市場出現一大班IT狗 &gt; 其他公司低價吸納 &gt;...<br />\n無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26aec22368862ae26823ae0f7e839a23557c910c","tid":610650,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"IT無用嘅 完全冇貢獻<br />\n改用人手最好"},{"pid":"b9d379e1ba653234ddad49a3bebc0eb5eaf30dfe","tid":610650,"uid":35815,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T10:08:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d866503e8b95f412ce7ed47887a5606e2bf6914","tid":610650,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T10:09:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1af9861ff7bedfb0c0becf1ed1b4e80cc1ee655","tid":610650,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T10:10:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04ba258f34ec3b89b71910f6788b57bd246361d9","tid":610650,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T11:17:34.000Z","msg":"支那人公司係咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a217272b95de29d9950f9171b8731357150a33","tid":610650,"uid":41382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22a28e6cbd0439b372b7b35c47f2b589eedfffd0","tid":610650,"uid":4525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"it 唔使放假咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"野又未做哂放咩假啊"},{"pid":"cc061d7af542de4aee5e3f6ac3ff62fbf9c40471","tid":610650,"uid":43008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b9d379e1ba653234ddad49a3bebc0eb5eaf30dfe","tid":610650,"uid":35815,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T10:08:45.000Z","msg":